title: Gionee launches dual-sim F103 smartphone at Rs 9,999
text:
Gionee launches dual-sim F103 smartphone at Rs 9,999 BT Online New Delhi Last Updated: September 2, 2015 | 14:27 IST 
Chinese firm Gionee has launched new F103 smartphone at Rs 9,999. The phone has a five-inch HD ISP display. The phone runs Android 5.0 Lollipop with Amigo 3.0 skin on top. 
It is powered by a 1.3-GHz Quad-Core, 64 Bit processor. The phone has 2 GB RAM and 16 GB ROM and supports 4G services. 
Its sports a 8.0 MP primary camera with LED flash and a 5 MP secondary camera. 
The phone also enables HD video recording. 
The phone has features such as face beauty, panorama (Horizontal), geo-tagging, touch focus, 20 Snaps In One Click, Pic Note,Take Anytime, Filters, HDR Mode, Take Anytime and Filter. 
The dual-SIM phone has a battery capacity of 2400 mAh. 
It has a standby time of 267 hours (4G), 185 hours (3G) and 240 hours (2G).
